Modifications in this distribution
----------------------------------
The Telsi distribution differs from upstream OpenFang only in
customer-facing static dashboard assets located in
crates/openfang-api/static/ (logo, favicon, manifest, head-tag title,
literal product-name strings, and theme colors). No source code, no
public APIs, no on-disk file paths, and no behavioral semantics have
been altered.

The names "OpenFang", "RightNow-AI", and any associated logos remain
trademarks of RightNow-AI. Per Apache 2.0 Section 6, this distribution
does not use those trademarks except as needed to truthfully describe
the origin of the upstream work in this NOTICE and in source-level
identifiers (file paths, JS class names, internal API endpoints) that
are part of the unmodified upstream interface.

The names "Telsi" and any associated logos are trademarks of Telsi
(telsi.ai) and are applied only to the customer-facing chrome of this
downstream distribution.

